name: Anders Wenngren
biography:
Born Stockholm, Sweden.
Graduated from architectural school, Stockholm, 1972.
c.1972-78  Worked as architect.
1979  Relocated to New York. 
1979--Freelance Illustrator. 
Shopping bag projects: In adddition to the present bag, one bag for Conran's, a series of bags for Seibu, Tokyo and one bag for Franc Franc, Tokyo.
